  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/633681/263123848-e99cc861-483d-4b53-a8ce-5d9c372d343b.png\" width=\"500\"/></p>\n\n<p>Wizard Vicuna is a 13B parameter model based on Llama 2 trained by MelodysDreamj.</p>\n\n<h3>CLI</h3>\n\n<p>Open the terminal and run <code>ollama run wizard-vicuna</code></p>\n\n<h3>API</h3>\n\n<p>Example:</p>\n\n<pre><code>curl -X POST http://localhost:11434/api/generate -d &#39;{\n  &#34;model&#34;: &#34;wizard-vicuna&#34;,\n  &#34;prompt&#34;:&#34;Why is the sky blue?&#34;\n }&#39;\n</code></pre>\n\n<h2>Memory requirements</h2>\n\n<ul>\n<li>13b models generally require at least 16GB of RAM</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Reference</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/TheBloke/wizard-vicuna-13B-GGML\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Bloke</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/junelee/wizard-vicuna-13b\" rel=\"nofollow\">MelodysDreamj</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
